    <span class="marquee-item">USB Flash</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">3D NAND</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">JEDEC Validated</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══ BRAND INTRO TILE — parchment ══ -->
<div class="tile tile-parchment">
  <div class="tile-inner">
    <h2 class="tile-h2 fade-in">One brand. A complete portfolio.</h2>
    <p class="tile-lead fade-in fade-in-delay-1">SSD, DRAM, GPU, and external storage — one partner covering consumer, commercial, and channel markets.</p>
    <p class="tile-body fade-in fade-in-delay-2">Structured product planning. Rigorous quality validation. End-to-end manufacturing control. Simorchip gives partners stable supply, dependable performance, and a portfolio that's ready to sell.</p>
  </div>
</div>

